# Peptides Deployment Guardrails

This repository is **Peptides only**. It must stay isolated from PetrolPricesNearMe, fitomelbourne, fitocreative, and any other unrelated projects.

## Hosting (required)

- **Primary:** Cloudflare Workers via OpenNext (`@opennextjs/cloudflare`)
- **Config:** `wrangler.jsonc` (worker name: `peptides`)
- **Build:** `npm run cf:build` → produces `.open-next/`
- **Deploy:** `npm run deploy` → `opennextjs-cloudflare build` + `wrangler deploy`
- **Local dev:** `npm run dev` (Next.js dev server)

## Never add or reference

- Vercel (`vercel.json`, `.vercel`, `VERCEL_*` env vars, Vercel deploy docs)
- PetrolPricesNearMe / petrol / fuel project names or credentials
- Unrelated GitHub repos, Cloudflare workers, or API tokens from other projects

## Environment

- Production URL: set `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` (e.g. `https://peptides4u.com`)
- Cloudflare auth: `CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN` + `CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID` in `.env.local` / `.dev.vars` (never commit)
- Payments: `NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PAYMENT_LINK` or `NEXT_PUBLIC_PAYMENT_LINK` per `lib/payments.ts`

## Stack (from peptides.md)

- Next.js 16, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui patterns
- Future: Supabase/Prisma, Sanity CMS, eWAY payments — not Vercel
